In this version you can now purchase an Annual Subscription of Lifetime Movie Club for just 39.99.

All Lifetime Movie Club members are now required to create a profile. If you are currently a subscriber but do not have a profile you can create one by navigating to the sign in section and tapping the RESTORE YOUR SUBSCRIPTION button then proceeding to create a Lifetime Movie Club profile. We have also fixed a few bugs and improved performance!

Hey Lifetime Movie fans! In this update we have a slick new video player that allows you to jump back into a movie from where you last left off. But wait there s more! We heard your feedback: AppleTV support is coming soon!
Hey Lifetime Movie Fans! In this update we fixed a few bugs and made some performance improvements. We heard your feedback AppleTV support is coming soon!

Hey Lifetime Movie Fans! Create a Movie Club profile to get Lifetime Movie Club access on ROKU and to become eligible for other benefits! We also fixed a few bugs and made some performance improvements.

Hey Lifetime Movie Fans! Here s what we have for you in our latest version: A Share button in the video player so you can tell your friends which movies you re watching! A bunch of small improvements to make the app run better and faster Have feedback for us We d love to hear from you please drop us a line at watchapps aenetworks.com

Hey Lifetime Movie fans! We have a bunch of improvements for you in this version: Airplay Support! Send your movies to the big screen with Airplay See where you left off in a movie with a new progress indicator Now you can see how long you have left to enjoy a movie We also made some performance improvements and fixed some bugs. Have feedback for us We d love to hear from you please drop us a line at watchapps aenetworks.com
